Hey All,
Because I was late on posting the fliers for the meeting I decided this would be the best alternative.  We are having a meeting tomorrow, I (Brian) am presenting on Operating System Independence.  Followed by the movie Iron Man, in BluRay if I can get it set up (not likely).  I hope you all can join me as I present cross platform solutions to being productive as a power user and a developer!  See you there!
-Brian Cullinan

Hi everyone! So my User Interfaces (CS477) group needs some data about people who live with roommates...if you could please take 2 minutes of your time and fill this out, we would greatly appreciate it!! C'mon, I know you all take the "Which Vampire Hottie Will You End Up Dating" Quizzes that are going around anyway, AND THIS ONES FOR CHARITY 

Please take this short (2 minute) survey if you have a roommate:
http://www.surveymonkey.com/s.aspx?sm=RlcGz002DyafRYZLB_2fJxeQ_3d_3d

THANK YOU GUYS SO MUCH

Facebook User
So I suppose it's only fair that I spread other surveys out for other UI teams...and honestly this group totally deserves two minutes of your time: they took some of the harshest criticism I've ever heard from Eck today and they could really use some help with this!! And yes, I've seen Palmer at Capstone! 
(Eck and Palmer are both members of this facebook group, so I kid...mostly)

Please be a hero today! You'd really be helping out a ton and it only takes 2 minutes!

http://spreadsheets.google.com/viewform?hl=en&formkey=cEVBRDVnSmt6VUNPdFVYVUx4eXQ3SWc6MA

THANK YOU GUYS SO MUCH! 
And if you see any of the group members, be generous with hugs!

Leah
